ize=1> I was AFK in Scarlett Desert without the AFK tag up....my bad.  Come back and Taj asks, you rezzing that guy?  What guy? I think as I scroll up.  Ah, there's a tell, so I respond, drag to plat, I'll rez....hey 100pp donation for 2 rezzes, np, I'm in downtime atm and fm. So the two corpses arrive, I rez, get paid, thank you very much.<br>
<br>
Then I notice the /ooc....some guy named Bagend &lt;Royal Blood&gt; is bad mouthing me for refusing to rez him when he's paying 100pp, for putting him on my ignore list, yada yada yada. Hmmmm, I just rezzed the guy and his bud that I got the tell from......<br>
<br>
I scroll up again to where I said going AFK.  No tells from Bagbutt.  So I nicely tell him in /ooc you never told me anything and sorry I was AFK without AFK tag up.  He calls me a liar, etc, etc.  He drags me corpse, yes, I'm nice, I STILL offered to rez him (hey he was gonna pay me 100pp).<br>
<br>
I did rez him, he did not pay.<br>
<br>
Moral of this story?  NEVER GO AROUND WITHOUT ROLEPLAY UP!!!  and, don't be so dam nice to loud mouth Bagbutt.  <br>
<br>
Dyann Truesite &lt;Hegemony&gt;<br>
